highlights.text: “Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 896 days straight.
“Retrovisor” by Gusttavo Lima is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #92.
Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Saudade De Quem Eu Sou - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #11.
“Cama Embrasa” by Felipe Amorim and Gustavo Mioto is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 71 spots at #102.
